English:
>... Stop! <color=red><size=200%>It's moving.</size></color>
>... I'll go behind it. 
>... Shit, they heard us!

French.Translation:
>... Stop ! <color=red><size=200%>Il est en train de bouger.</size></color>
>... Je vais me faufiler derrière lui.
>... Merde, ils nous ont entendus !

Italian.Translation:
>… Fermi! <color=red><size=200%>Si sta muovendo.</size></color>
>… Ci vado dietro. 
>… Merda, ci hanno sentito!

German.Translation:
>… Stopp! <color=red><size=200%>Es bewegt sich.</size></color>
>… Ich werde mich dahinter stellen. 
>… Scheiße, sie haben uns gehört!

Spanish.Translation:
> ¡Alto! <color=red><size=200%>Se está moviendo.</size></color>
> Iré detrás. 
>... ¡Mierda, nos han escuchado!

Portuguese_Brazil.Translation:
>... Parem! <color=red><size=200%>Está se movendo.</size></color>
>... Vou por trás. 
>... Merda, nos ouviram!

Polish.Translation:
>... Stać! <color=red><size=200%>Rusza się.</size></color>
>... Zajdę go od tyłu. 
>... Usłyszeli, psiamać!

Japanese.Translation:
>... 止まれ！<color=red><size=200%>動いている。</size></color>
>... 後をつけよう。
>... クソッ、奴らに聞かれた！

Korean.Translation:
>... 멈춰! <color=red><size=200%>움직인다.</size></color>
>... 내가 뒤로 갈게. 
>... 젠장, 들켰어!

Chinese_Traditional.Translation:
>... 停下！<color=red><size=200%>它在動。</size></color>
>... 我去後面。
>... 該死，我們被聽到聲音了！

Chinese_Simplified.Translation:
>... 停下！<color=red><size=200%>它在动。</size></color>
